{"title":"hexo部署到服务器的踩坑","uid":"cb3148bb5594e316eaf5e1e4e87fd84c","slug":"hexo部署到服务器的踩坑","date":"2024-03-23T07:49:09.000Z","updated":"2024-03-23T08:27:00.398Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo部署到服务器的踩坑.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h3 id=\"因为是第一次使用hexo部署服务器所以遇到了许多坑-，记下来以供参考\"><a href=\"#因为是第一次使用hexo部署服务器所以遇到了许多坑-，记下来以供参考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"因为是第一次使用hexo部署服务器所以遇到了许多坑 ，记下来以供参考\"></a>因为是第一次使用hexo部署服务器所以遇到了许多坑 ，记下来以供参考</h3><p>配置:centos7  2核2G<br>需要安装的东西:nginx，git和xshell</p>\n<h3 id=\"连接云服务器\"><a href=\"#连接云服务器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"连接云服务器\"></a>连接云服务器</h3><p>较为简单，不必多说自行百度</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装nginx\"><a href=\"#安装nginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装nginx\"></a>安装nginx</h3><p>nginx的安装较为简单，首先检查安装nginx所需要的环境</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#查看 C++ 环境是否安装</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">gcc -v</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#查看 zlib 是否安装</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">cat /usr/lib64/pkgconfig/zlib.pc</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#查看 pcre 是否安装</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">pcre-config --version</span></span></code></pre></div><p>配置nginx安装时所需要的运行环境</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#一次安装4个插件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">yum -y install gcc pcre pcre-devel zlib zlib-devel openssl openssl-devel</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#如果上面的安装错误可以试一下分开安装（注:上面安装成功了的话下面的直接跳过）</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">======================================================================</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">     #安装 nginx 需要先将官网下载的源码进行编译，编译依赖 gcc 环境</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">yum install gcc-c++</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">     #pcre是一个perl库，包括perl兼容的正则表达式库，nginx的http模块使用pcre来解析正则表达式，所以需要安装pcre库</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">yum install -y pcre pcre-devel</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">     #zlib库提供了很多种压缩和解压缩方式nginx使用zlib对http包的内容进行gzip，所以需要安装</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">yum install -y zlib zlib-devel</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">     #nginx 不仅支持 http 协议，还支持 https（即在ssl协议上传输http），所以需要在 Centos 安装 OpenSSL 库</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">yum install -y openssl openssl-devel</span></span></code></pre></div><h6 id=\"安装-nginx注意\"><a href=\"#安装-nginx注意\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 nginx注意\"></a>安装 nginx注意</h6><p>方法一：在官网直接下载.tar.gz安装包，然后通过远程工具拉取到 linux 里面【在 &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local 里面创建个nginx文件夹，拉进来。（也可以拉到其他地方）注意：如果没有十足把握还是选择方法二，亲身经历】<br>+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br>方法二：使用wget命令下载，确保系统已经安装了wget，如果没有安装，执行 yum install wget 安装。</p>\n<h6 id=\"使用方法二安装\"><a href=\"#使用方法二安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用方法二安装\"></a>使用方法二安装</h6><p>cd进入usr&#x2F;local 里面创建 nginx 文件夹以后方便管理</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#进入usr下的local目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">cd usr/local</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#在local目录下创建 mysql 文件夹</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">mkdir nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#进入nginx目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">cd nginx</span></span></code></pre></div><h6 id=\"通过wegt下载nginx压缩包\"><a href=\"#通过wegt下载nginx压缩包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过wegt下载nginx压缩包\"></a>通过wegt下载nginx压缩包</h6><div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">wget https://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.21.6.tar.gz</span></span></code></pre></div><h6 id=\"解压下载的nginx安装包并进入解压后的文件夹\"><a href=\"#解压下载的nginx安装包并进入解压后的文件夹\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解压下载的nginx安装包并进入解压后的文件夹\"></a>解压下载的nginx安装包并进入解压后的文件夹</h6><div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#解压</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">tar xvf nginx-1.21.6.tar.gz</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#进入解压后的目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">cd nginx-1.21.6</span></span></code></pre></div><h6 id=\"配置nginx（注：需要进入解压之后的nginx文件夹）\"><a href=\"#配置nginx（注：需要进入解压之后的nginx文件夹）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置nginx（注：需要进入解压之后的nginx文件夹）\"></a>配置nginx（注：需要进入解压之后的nginx文件夹）</h6><div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">./configure --prefix=/usr/local/nginx --with-http_stub_status_module --with-http_ssl_module</span></span></code></pre></div><h6 id=\"编译-安装\"><a href=\"#编译-安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编译  安装\"></a>编译  安装</h6><div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#编译</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">make</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#安装</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">make install</span></span></code></pre></div><h6 id=\"启动nginx-关闭nginx\"><a href=\"#启动nginx-关闭nginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启动nginx 关闭nginx\"></a>启动nginx 关闭nginx</h6><div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">###启动nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">cd /usr/local/nginx/sbin</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#启动nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">./nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">#关闭nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">./nginx -s stop</span></span></code></pre></div><p>出现下图代表安装成功可以进行后续操作<img src=\"/image/nginx%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装git\"><a href=\"#安装git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装git\"></a>安装git</h3>","feature":true,"text":"因为是第一次使用hexo部署服务器所以遇到了许多坑 ，记下来以供参考配置:centos7 2核2G需要安装的东西:nginx，git和xshell 连接